Date: 2023-09-15 12:16:10 +0000</comment>
                            <comment id="14611470" author="dfuchs" created="Fri, 15 Sep 2023 03:28:32 -0700"  >The java/net/httpclient/HttpClientLocalAddrTest.java fails relatively frequently in timeout - and the log shows the pinned thread above.&lt;br/&gt;
Whether that&amp;#39;s the root cause of the test failure is hard to say, but we should fix the code to avoid pinned threads. This one path that had escaped my notice before. </comment>
